{"tid":1491154,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李澤楷重申，強烈反對暴力，希望警方「有能力」將暴徒繩之於法。","createTime":"2019-08-20T10:12:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T11:53:12.000Z","uid":33307,"like":16,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"56b1a05d79bebe61769361a28708e3ebf2612e45","tid":1491154,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T10:12:22.000Z","msg":"細仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n警方在羅湖口岸拘捕一名50歲涉案男子，涉及凌晨發生的將軍澳斬人案，疑犯涉嫌傷人，正被拘留調查。事件有一男兩女受傷，其中最嚴重，背部及肩部受傷的26歲女子，在醫院深切治療部留醫，情況危殆。信報證實是信報副刊記者，月初已辭職，正在放大假。信報譴責任何暴力，對同事受傷表示痛心。盈科拓展主席李澤楷向傷者家人深切慰問，並表示會支付受襲記者的一切醫療及復康開支，祝願她早日康復。<span style=\"color: red;\">李澤楷重申，強烈反對暴力，希望警方有能力將暴徒繩之於法。</span><br />\n<br />\n警察公共關係科總警司謝振中重申，絕對不接受所有暴力行為，不論涉案人或受害人背景，警方都會不偏不倚調查。"},{"pid":"e299fd6b5e5c39064b1099a3f91be2fd5b39976d","tid":1491154,"uid":33307,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T10:13:57.000Z","msg":"竟然質疑黑警能力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd2e9fab09d7e9528c1d1b58ce2d4c30b7aa6cf7","tid":1491154,"uid":39550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T10:14:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3294731b0d83113768a420e56d08bd798452b223","tid":1491154,"uid":35580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T10:17:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e2a1e8b863993022cd3b07a20e24e2076d5b02a","tid":1491154,"uid":21141,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e299fd6b5e5c39064b1099a3f91be2fd5b39976d","tid":1491154,"uid":33307,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T10:13:57.000Z","msg":"竟然質疑黑警能力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.